conbody.p:
Recording are saved as idllab\Teacher\recordings\YYYY-MM-DDTHH-mm-ss.{wav|ogg|flac} files, where


Teacher is teacher name in advanced mode (see _fixme_ [xref]) and is omitted in beginner mode;

YYYY, MM, DD are year, month, and date of the recording;

HH, mm, and ss are hours, minutes and seconds of the start of the recording.
